				<outline text="What's the real story??" created="Thu, 06 Dec 2007 01:10:19 GMT">
					<outline text="Bush and Cheney knew what was going to be in the NIE for months. That's not a stretch. It's completely unbelievable that they didn't ask or weren't told what was coming. " created="Thu, 06 Dec 2007 01:10:21 GMT"/>
					<outline text="They tried to drum up support for a war anyway. " created="Thu, 06 Dec 2007 01:10:53 GMT"/>
					<outline text="Hoping to rush us to war. Then the NIE would come out and they'd say that no one knew that there was no nuclear program in Iran." created="Thu, 06 Dec 2007 01:11:06 GMT"/>
					<outline text="The only question is why they didn't start the bombing." created="Thu, 06 Dec 2007 01:11:41 GMT"/>
					<outline text="Could it be that they gave the order and the military didn't do it?" created="Thu, 06 Dec 2007 01:11:54 GMT"/>
					<outline text="In the meantime one has to wonder why the French president Sarkozy was saying the same things about Iran along with Cheney and Bush." created="Thu, 06 Dec 2007 01:12:31 GMT"/>
					<outline text="There's a back-story we're not hearing." created="Thu, 06 Dec 2007 01:13:05 GMT"/>
					</outline>
